Description: scMaSigPro is a polynomial regression-based approach inspired by
    the MaSigPro Bioconductor package. It discretizes the expression of
    individual cells along pseudotime while preserving the order of cells.
    Subsequently, it applies the maSigPro model to identify genes exhibiting
    significant expression profile differences among branching paths.
